00:08:07.230 --> 00:08:10.410 align:middle line:84%
times more fundamental and a
million times more powerful

00:08:10.410 --> 00:08:11.910 align:middle line:90%
than the chemical level.

00:08:11.910 --> 00:08:14.130 align:middle line:84%
So the deeper you go,
the smaller you go,

00:08:14.130 --> 00:08:17.940 align:middle line:84%
